# shadcn/ui Usage

- Use shadcn/ui for all UI elements in this project.
- If shadcn/ui is not initialized, run:

```bash
pnpm dlx shadcn@latest init --template next
```

- If a needed component is not installed, add it with `pnpm dlx shadcn@latest add <component>`.
- For example, to install the button component, run:

```bash
pnpm dlx shadcn@latest add button
```
